    <string name="dialog_title_notifications">Setup notifications</string>
    <string name="dialog_text_notifications">
        For better work of application notifications you need do 3 things:\n\n1. Turn ON autostart
        in \"App settings\". It allow us display your status bar notifications after device
        restart.\n2. Turn OFF battery restriction (battery saver) in \"App settings\". It allow to
        display notifications in status bar even when you close app.\n3.Turn OFF \"show
        notifications\" for Eternal service. This service allows app not to miss your
        notifications.\n\nFor first and second option use \"App settings\" button, for third -
        use \"Hide service\" button.
    </string>
